.com%2Fhkautonomy2020%2Fstatus%2F1255376603099652097%3Fs%3D21&h=f781efbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hkautonomy2020/status/1255376603099652097?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\nTwitter"}]}